{"tid":1641743,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"求助 小露寶唔食嘢成日訓","createTime":"2019-10-09T12:27:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T13:10:12.000Z","uid":174260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba9ad64dd4fc62508011337b6fc196d7a46c9c95","tid":1641743,"uid":174260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T12:27:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ca0ELur.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fca0ELur.jpg&h=15966901&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢隻小露寶係領養返嚟，女仔，上手話4個月大，開頭接佢返嚟嗰兩日好活潑、好精神，好鍾意玩跑輪，但最近幾日開始唔食野唔飲水，連舊糧都唔食，又唔玩跑輪，睇完獸醫都搵唔到個病因。勉強同佢打咗皮下水，同埋用針筒餵食住先，尋晚好似精神番。<br />\n不過今日發現佢隻眼(如圖)好似開唔到，行動變得好遲緩，日夜都訓，有冇人知佢究竟發生咩事？求解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7805d7055502352c105c0a7b13edb7d72e9f6e6","tid":1641743,"uid":263913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T13:10:12.000Z","msg":"睇多一兩個獸醫啦"}]}